    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You send negative energy coursing through a creature that you can see within range, causing it searing pain. The target must make a [[/save constitution]] save. It takes [[/damage 7d8 + 30 necrotic]] damage on a failed save, or half as much damage on a success.</p><p>A Humanoid killed by this spell rises as a <strong>zombie</strong> at the start of your next turn. The zombie is permanently under your command and follows your verbal orders to the best of its ability.</p>",
